yaml-cpp is a YAML parser and emitter in C++
matching the YAML 1.2 spec.

This SlackBuild uses version 0.6.3 (last of the 0.6.x series)
for use by SlackBuilds not able to use later versions, in
particular FreeCAD-1.0.2 which needs 0.6.3.

NOTE: yaml-cpp conflict with yaml-cpp0.3 and yaml-cpp
You must NOT install both of them on one system.
